1 dela ys in acquiring goods and services fundamental to generating
2 this revenue.
3 D. No exemption provided in this section shall be construed for
4 the use of leasing or contracting for state-owned restaurants in
5 Oklahoma state parks.
6 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
